Application: Cascade Optional FK
  Description: Non-required cascade reference for NULL-FK cascade behavior
Id: a1c0c1a0-cade-4a00-9000-000000000003

Identity:
  Scopes are "opt.view", "opt.manage", "opt.delete"
  A "tester" has "opt.view", "opt.manage", and "opt.delete"

Content called "categories":
  Each category has a name which is text, required
  Anyone with "opt.view" can view categories
  Anyone with "opt.manage" can create categories
  Anyone with "opt.delete" can delete categories

Content called "items":
  Each item has a label which is text, required
  Each item has a category which references categories, cascade on delete
  Anyone with "opt.view" can view items
  Anyone with "opt.manage" can create items
